ation between\nsynchrotron peak frequency and synchrotron curvature in gamma-NLS1s is large\nthan that of FSRQs and BL Lacs. This result may imply that the cooling\ndominates over the acceleration process for FSRQs and BL Lacs, while\ngamma-NLS1s is the opposite.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Dec 2020 09:04:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-03"}
