ic technique is $O(C)$-competitive. Hence, our algorithms\nare constant-competitive whenever the accuracy $C$ is a constant.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Dec 2020 10:31:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-09"}
